OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773864689
OL,3,CAldershot couple jailed for running
OL,4,Chuman trafficking and prostitution ring
OL,6,FWATCH: Police bodycam footage captures
OL,7,Fthe moment that Wei Gong Li and Yafeng
OL,8,FDong are arrested
OL,10,FA husband and wife have been jailed
OL,11,Ffor a combined total of almost five
OL,12,Fyears for running a human trafficking
OL,13,Fand prostitution operation in
OL,14,FAldershot.
OL,16,FWei-Gong Li, 45, and Yafeng Dong, 53,
OL,17,Fwere handed prison sentences of two
OL,18,Fyears and one month, and two years and
OL,19,Feight months respectively.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
