OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773864689
OL,3,CAldershot couple jailed for running
OL,4,Chuman trafficking and prostitution ring
OL,6,FThe pair used two addresses - one in
OL,7,FAldershot and one in Guildford - for
OL,8,Fprostitution. They transported women
OL,9,Fto the addresses to meet people who
OL,10,Fpaid for sex.
OL,12,FHampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,13,FConstabulary originally launched an
OL,14,Finvestigation in November 2023, after
OL,15,Fa safety concern was raised at an
OL,16,Faddress in Ascot Court, Aldershot.
OL,18,FA lone woman was found inside the main
OL,19,Fbedroom, which contained lingerie and
OL,20,Fcondoms, when police conducted a
OL,21,Fsearch of the property.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
