PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773864689
OL,3,CAldershot couple jailed for running
OL,4,Chuman trafficking and prostitution ring
OL,6,FExaminations of mobile phones
OL,7,Frecovered by police later confirmed
OL,8,Fthat Li and Dong had managed the
OL,9,Fbrothels, arranged payments and moved
OL,10,Fwomen between properties.
OL,12,FDetective Sergeant Paul Jarrett, from
OL,13,Fthe Serious and Organised Crime Unit,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Wei-Gong Li and Yafeng Dong
OL,15,Fwere involved in an organised criminal
OL,16,Fenterprise which targeted and
OL,17,Fexploited vulnerable women.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
