FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773864689
OL,3,CAldershot couple jailed for running
OL,4,Chuman trafficking and prostitution ring
OL,6,F"The women were controlled and used
OL,7,Ffor sex work purely for the financial
OL,8,Fgain of the couple - and our
OL,9,Finvestigations found they had #182,385
OL,10,Fin cash deposits.
OL,12,F"Our officers take reports of modern
OL,13,Fslavery, human trafficking and
OL,14,Fexploitation extremely seriously and
OL,15,Fwill do everything we can to put those
OL,16,Fresponsible before the courts."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
